official_title: A bill to amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1954 to subject Federal land banks, Federal land bank associations, and Federal intermediate credit banks to the taxes imposed by such code.

summary.text: Subjects Federal land banks, Federal land bank associations, and Federal intermediate credit banks to corporate taxes imposed by the Internal Revenue Code of 1954. (Amends 26 U.S.C. 501)
